[thinking] I'm trying to figure out how to work with a custom ClassLoader when test classes are in the system loader. I wonder if I can use dynamic class loading in a native setup. If the parent doesn't have a class, but the addon ClassLoader does, could I use `ClassLoader.loadClass`? It seems like `Class.forName` could fail while `loadClass` might succeed by returning an existing class for a different name. This could be an interesting way to exercise the ClassLoader's functionality without defining new classes at runtime!
[thinking] 
